---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Picture, Img } from "astro-imagetools/components";
---

<Layout title="AZTECA Home Services">
  <main>
    <section
      class="relative flex h-[80vh] flex-col justify-end bg-army-900 sm:justify-center"
    >
      <div class="hero contents">
        <Picture
          src="/landscape/general2.webp"
          alt="Beautiful clean sparkling pool"
          objectFit="cover"
          objectPosition="top center"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute z-10 flex flex-col gap-4 p-4 lg:p-8">
        <h2
          class="max-w-[600px] rounded bg-army-50/60 p-4 text-3xl text-army-900 drop-shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
          <b>Say Goodbye to Pests</b>, <b>Hello to a Sparkling Pool</b> and yes to
          a <b>Well-Manicured Landscape</b>
        </h2>
        <a
          class="w-fit rounded border-b-8 border-army-300 bg-army-900 p-4 pb-3 text-lg font-bold text-army-50 drop-shadow-2xl transition-colors hover:bg-army-300"
          href="/contact"
          >Schedule an Appointment
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside
      class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-4 bg-army-400 p-4 md:grid-cols-3 lg:p-8"
    >
      <h4 class="py-[14px] text-2xl font-light text-army-50 md:col-span-2">
        Contact us for a free estimate
      </h4>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="col-span-1 rounded bg-army-900 px-2 py-4 text-center text-lg font-bold uppercase text-army-50 transition-[background] hover:bg-army-300"
        >Contact Us</a
      >
    </aside>

    <section class="p-4 pb-4 lg:p-8">
      <h4 class="col-span-12 py-2 text-3xl font-black uppercase">
        Our Services
      </h4>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 text-xl">
        <li class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <object width="40px" height="40px" data="/general/bug.svg" type=""
            ></object>
            <h5 class="whitespace-nowrap py-2 font-bold">Pest Control</h5>
          </div>
          <div>
            AZTECA offers comprehensive pest control for homes and businesses,
            including, but not limited to, <u>termites</u>, <u>birds</u>, <u
              >scorpions</u
            >, <u>roaches</u>, <u>spiders</u>, <u>home seal</u>, <u>bed bugs</u
            >, <u>fleas</u>, <u>flies</u>, <u>mosquitoes</u>, <u>rodents</u>,
            and <u>bees</u>. With <b>over 10 years of experience</b> using <em
              >integrated pest management</em
            >, we have a proven track record of successfully eradicating pest
            issues.


          </div>
          <a
          href="/pest-control"
          class="rounded border-b-8 border-army-400 bg-army-900 px-2 py-4 text-center text-lg font-bold uppercase text-army-50 transition-[background] hover:bg-army-300"
          >Pest Control</a
        >
        </li>

        <li class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <object
              width="40px"
              height="40px"
              data="/general/shovel.svg"
              type=""></object>
            <h5 class="whitespace-nowrap py-2 font-bold">Landscaping</h5>
          </div>
          <div>
            We offer <u>general maintenance</u>, <u>landscape installation</u>, <u
              >pavers</u
            >, <u>synthetic grass</u>, <u>sod</u>, <u
              >irrigration install/repair</u
            >, <u>tree removal/trimming</u> by <b>certified arborists</b>, <u
              >weed control</u
            >,
            <u>reseeding</u> and <u><em>more</em></u>! Whatever you need to keep
            your yard, lawn, or commercial landscaping in shape, we can do it!
          </div>
          <a
            href="/landscaping"
            class="rounded border-b-8 border-army-400 bg-army-900 px-2 py-4 text-center text-lg font-bold uppercase text-army-50 transition-[background] hover:bg-army-300"
            >Landscaping</a
          >
        </li>
        <li class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <object width="40px" height="40px" data="/general/pool.svg" type=""
            ></object>
            <h5 class="whitespace-nowrap py-2 font-bold">Pool Services</h5>
          </div>
          <div>
            <u>Chemical balancing & testing</u>, <u>green-to-cleans</u>, <u
              >vacuuming & cleaning</u
            >, <u>algae prevention & removal</u>, <u>filter cleaning</u>, <u
              >sand changes</u
            >, <u>pool acid washes</u>, <u>tile cleaning</u>, <u
              >equipment repairs</u
            > and
            <u><em>more</em></u>! All of our services are performed by CPO
            certified technicians to ensure the highest level of quality and
            professionalism.
          </div>
          <a
              href="/pools"
              class="rounded border-b-8 border-army-400 bg-army-900 px-2 py-4 text-center text-lg font-bold uppercase text-army-50 transition-[background] hover:bg-army-300"
              >Pools</a
            >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- <hr class="my-3 border-army-300 mx-4" /> -->

    <section class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-8 p-4 pt-0 lg:gap-16 lg:p-8">
      <div class="col-span-12">
        <h5 class="py-3 text-3xl font-black uppercase">Why AZTECA?</h5>
        <ul class="text-xl">
          <li>&check; Dedicated to Quality, Workmanship and Service</li>
          <li>&check; Licensed, Bonded and Insured</li>
          <li>&check; 100% Veteran Owned Business</li>
          <li>&check; Best in Industry Service / Customer Care Practices</li>
          <li>&check; Unmatched Service and Customer Care Practices</li>
          <li>
            &check; Azteca is a nominee with Ranking Arizona as one of the
            <em>Top Family-Owned Businesses</em>.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="col-span-12 text-lg">
        <h5 class="py-2 text-3xl font-black uppercase">Office Hours</h5>
        <ul>
          <li>Monday - Friday: 8:00am - 3:00pm</li>
        </ul>
        <span>Call now:</span>
        <a class="whitespace-nowrap font-bold underline" href="tel:602-926-2021"
          >602-926-2021</a
        >
      </div>

      <div class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-12">
        <h5 class="py-2 text-3xl font-black uppercase">Testimonials</h5>
        <div class="flex justify-center fill-army-600 py-2">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            class="h-[40px] w-[40px]"
          >
            <path d="m12 17 6 4-1-7 5-5h-7l-3-7-3 7H2l5 5-1 7z"></path>
          </svg>
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            class="h-[40px] w-[40px]"
          >
            <path d="m12 17 6 4-1-7 5-5h-7l-3-7-3 7H2l5 5-1 7z"></path>
          </svg>
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            class="h-[40px] w-[40px]"
          >
            <path d="m12 17 6 4-1-7 5-5h-7l-3-7-3 7H2l5 5-1 7z"></path>
          </svg>
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            class="h-[40px] w-[40px]"
          >
            <path d="m12 17 6 4-1-7 5-5h-7l-3-7-3 7H2l5 5-1 7z"></path>
          </svg>
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            class="h-[40px] w-[40px]"
          >
            <path d="m12 17 6 4-1-7 5-5h-7l-3-7-3 7H2l5 5-1 7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="grid w-full grid-flow-row gap-8 sm:grid-flow-col">
          <blockquote class="h-min border-l-[6px] border-army-600 pl-4">
            "Wonderful customer service and awesome techs. They make sure to
            address all of your concerns and make sure they do all they can to
            help. Will never use a different company again."
            <br /><br />
            - Ashley L.
          </blockquote>
          <blockquote class="h-min border-l-[6px] border-army-600 pl-4">
            "These guys are fantastic! Reasonably prices. Great service!
            Beautiful work!"
            <br /><br />
            - John S.
          </blockquote>
          <blockquote class="h-min border-l-[6px] border-army-600 pl-4">
            " My pool looks fantastic no matter how many kids I've had in it
            over the weekend! I appreciate the ease of business and the
            scheduling phone calls of when my landscaping will take place. It
            makes it so much easier to plan around. Thanks for the care and
            detail that is put into the service."
            <br /><br />
            - Michelle G.
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside
      class="my-4 grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-4 bg-army-400 p-4 md:grid-cols-3 lg:p-8"
    >
      <h4 class="py-[14px] text-2xl font-light text-army-50 md:col-span-2">
        Ready to schedule an appointment?
      </h4>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="col-span-1 rounded bg-army-900 px-2 py-4 text-center text-lg font-bold uppercase text-army-50 transition-[background] hover:bg-army-300"
        >Contact Us</a
      >
    </aside>

    <section
      class="bg-[url('/general/aztecaCalendarOutline.svg')] bg-contain bg-no-repeat p-4 lg:p-8"
    >
      <h4 class="py-4 text-3xl font-black uppercase">AZTECA Home Services</h4>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4">
        <img
          class="col-span-12 w-full max-w-[400px] rounded drop-shadow-lg sm:col-span-5"
          src="/landscape/grass5.webp"
          alt="Azteca Employees Working"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <p class="col-span-12 text-xl sm:col-span-5">
          AZTECA Home Services is a full-service company that offers a wide
          variety of services to help maintain the necessities of your home and
          business. We offer individual services such as <a
            class="font-bold underline"
            href="/pest-control">pest control</a
          >, <a class="font-bold underline" href="/landscaping">landscaping</a>,
          and <a class="font-bold underline" href="/pools"
            >pool maintenance and repair</a
          >. For those that need full services, we have made it convenient for
          our clients to <em>bundle your services and save you money</em>. You
          will be able to rely on us to handle all of these services during your
          scheduled appointment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="bg-[url('/general/days/Wind.svg')] bg-contain bg-right-bottom bg-no-repeat p-4 lg:p-8"
    >
      <h4 class="py-4 text-3xl font-black uppercase">Areas We Serve</h4>
      <div class="citiesLists grid grid-cols-12 text-lg">
        <ul class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-6 md:col-span-3">
          <li>Anthem</li>
          <li>El Mirage</li>
          <li>New River</li>
          <li>Scottsdale</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-6 md:col-span-3">
          <li>Black Canyon City</li>
          <li>Glendale</li>
          <li>Pardise Valley</li>
          <li>Sun City</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-6 md:col-span-3">
          <li>Glendale</li>
          <li>Luke AFB</li>
          <li>Peoria</li>
          <li>Sun City West</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-6 md:col-span-3">
          <li>Cave Creek</li>
          <li>Morristown</li>
          <li>Phoenix</li>
          <li>Surprise</li>
          <li>Youngtown</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside
      class="my-4 grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-4 bg-army-400 p-4 md:grid-cols-3 lg:p-8"
    >
      <h4 class="py-[14px] text-2xl font-light text-army-50 md:col-span-2">
        Book your appointment now!
      </h4>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="col-span-1 rounded bg-army-900 px-2 py-4 text-center text-lg font-bold uppercase text-army-50 transition-[background] hover:bg-army-300"
        >Contact Us</a
      >
    </aside>

    <section class="flex flex-col gap-4 p-4 text-lg lg:gap-8 lg:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase">About the Owner</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 sm:gap-4">
        <img
          class="col-span-12 w-full max-w-[640px] rounded-t drop-shadow-lg sm:col-span-4 sm:max-w-[400px] sm:rounded"
          src="/dad/volunteering.webp"
          alt="Frankie Volunteering"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <img
          class="col-span-6 w-full max-w-[640px] rounded-bl drop-shadow-lg sm:col-span-4 sm:max-w-[400px] sm:rounded"
          src="/dad/foodBank.webp"
          alt="Frankie at a Food Bank"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <img
          class="col-span-6 w-full max-w-[640px] rounded-br drop-shadow-lg sm:col-span-4 sm:max-w-[400px] sm:rounded"
          src="/dad/donatingBlood.webp"
          alt="Frankie donating Blood"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <p class="max-w-prose">
        Meet Frankie Ruiz, the proud owner of Azteca Home Services. Frankie
        opened the business in 2012 with the goal of providing exceptional pest,
        pool, and landscaping services, all while spending more quality time
        with his family. He is the proud father of three children, Xavier,
        Diego, and Savannah, and loves nothing more than spending time with
        them. When he's not working, Frankie enjoys riding his motorcycle or
        enjoying a cold beer with his friends and family.
      </p>
      <p class="max-w-prose">
        Frankie's dedication to his community runs deep, and it's evident in his
        commitment to giving back. He is a veteran and takes great pride in his
        service to his country. Additionally, Frankie is actively involved in
        community efforts such as food drives, blood donations, and volunteer
        work. He truly appreciates the opportunities his business provides, and
        he is dedicated to serving both his clients and his community.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
<style>
  .citiesLists ul {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    /* justify-content: center; */
    /* align-items: center; */
  }
  .citiesLists ul li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
